New EnterprisesThe exemptions from the renewal of approvals are not covered under the MSME Ordinance 2019. The exemptions under the Ordinance are applicable only on the new enterprise and that includes an enterprise set up or proposed to be set up by an existing enterprise for manufacturing products or providing services at a location which is separately identifiable and different from location of the existing enterprise.For more details, visit the official website at https://rajudyogmitra.rajasthan.gov.in/  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: rajudyogmitra.rajasthan.gov.in  at  "}